## 6. Card 스타일 가이드

### 메인 카드 (Main Card)

```tsx
import { Card, CardHeader, CardTitle, CardContent } from "@/components/ui/card"
import { FileText } from "lucide-react"

<Card className="rounded-3xl border bg-card shadow-[0_8px_32px_rgba(130,170,227,0.18)] dark:border-[#343A50] dark:shadow-none">
  <CardHeader>
    <CardTitle>
      <FileText className="h-5 w-5" />
      카드 제목
    </CardTitle>
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent>
    {/* 컨텐츠 */}
  </CardContent>
</Card>
```

**사양 요약**

- **Card**: `h-full flex flex-col bg-card rounded-3xl border` + 라이트 블루 그림자 / 다크 `dark:border-[#343A50] dark:shadow-none`
- **CardHeader**: `h-12 px-4 py-0 border-b bg-muted/30 flex flex-row items-center justify-between`
- **CardTitle**: `text-lg font-bold flex items-center gap-2 leading-none`
- **CardContent**: `flex-1 min-h-0 flex flex-col gap-[3px] p-4 overflow-auto`
- **아이콘**: `h-5 w-5`

### 서브 카드 (Sub Card)

```tsx
<Card className="flex flex-col overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-[#343637] dark:border-[#343A50] shadow-[0_4px_24px_rgba(130,170,227,0.12)] dark:shadow-none">
  <CardHeader className="h-8 px-3 py-0">
    <CardTitle className="text-xs font-bold">서브 카드 제목</CardTitle>
  </CardHeader>
  <CardContent className="p-2">{/* 컨텐츠 */}</CardContent>
</Card>
```

