- **DialogHeader**: `h-12 px-4 py-0 border-b bg-muted/30 flex flex-row items-center justify-between space-y-0`
- **DialogTitle**: `text-lg font-bold flex items-center gap-2 leading-none`

**서브 카드 (내부 구획)**

- **Card**: `flex flex-col overflow-hidden border border-[#343637] dark:border-[#6b7280] shadow-md` (또는 메인 카드와 동일하게 블루 톤 그림자로 통일 가능)
- **CardHeader**: `h-8 px-3 py-0 border-b bg-muted/30 flex flex-row items-center justify-between border-[#343637] dark:border-[#6b7280]`
- **CardTitle**: `text-xs font-bold`
- **CardContent**: `p-2`
- **Textarea/Input**: `text-xs bg-card border-[#343637] dark:border-[#6b7280] resize-none`

