## 9. 탭 (Tabs)

- **TabsList**: `grid grid-cols-2 h-9 mb-[3px] bg-muted/40 dark:bg-gray-800/60 border border-[#343637] dark:border-[#6b7280] p-1`
- **TabsTrigger 기본**: `text-xs font-bold text-muted-foreground hover:bg-muted/60 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/60`
- **TabsTrigger 활성**: `data-[state=active]:bg-primary data-[state=active]:text-primary-foreground data-[state=active]:shadow-none`
- **주의**: `font-weight` 변경으로 레이아웃이 흔들리지 않도록 기본 `font-bold` 유지.

